translate french marip4_396c4a27:

    # fr "Not really."
    fr "Pas vraiment."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:14
translate french marip4_a3a6e94e:

    # fr "I talk to some people online and we meet occasionally."
    fr "Je discute avec certaines personnes en ligne et on se voit de temps en temps."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:15
translate french marip4_bb06b846:

    # fr "Then there is Jackson and Connie at work, a couple of people that I chat with at the vet clinic."
    fr "Et puis il y a Jackson et Connie au travail, deux personnes avec qui je discute à la clinique vétérinaire."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:17
translate french marip4_f4e0d40e:

    # fr "And you, of course."
    fr "Et toi, bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:18
translate french marip4_aefff0dc:

    # fr "I wouldn't say any of those relationships are close."
    fr "Je ne dirais pas que ces relations sont proches."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:19
translate french marip4_3c863e30:

    # fr "At least not yet."
    fr "Du moins, pas encore."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:24
translate french marip4_36d8c862:

    # fr "Not as close as I would like to be."
    fr "Pas aussi proches que je le voudrais."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:26
translate french marip4_a14f7e23:

    # fr "Still though, thank you for saying so."
    fr "Mais quand même, merci de le dire."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:30
translate french marip4_4b65bcb5:

    # fr "It definitely is!"
    fr "C'est tout à fait vrai !"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:31
translate french marip4_93b501c6:

    # fr "Everybody is always so busy with their own things, it's hard to keep up with everything going on in other people's lives."
    fr "Tout le monde est toujours tellement occupé par ses propres affaires qu’il est difficile de suivre tout ce qui se passe dans la vie des autres."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:32
translate french marip4_0dd5ba27:

    # pc "Very true."
    pc "C’est bien vrai."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:34
translate french marip4_5292c0c6:

    # fr "But I do wish that I had a couple of close friends that I could confide in."
    fr "Mais j’aimerais bien avoir quelques amis proches à qui je pourrais me confier."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:36
translate french marip4_7199f799:

    # fr "Maybe some day."
    fr "Peut-être un jour."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:39
translate french marip4_7567a5a5:

    # fr "Yeah, I guess so."
    fr "Ouais, je suppose."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:40
translate french marip4_fe109b44:

    # fr "What a loser huh?"
    fr "Quel loser, hein ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:42
translate french marip4_ea2dcc2a:

    # fr "I will eventually. It's just hard to find nice people who share your interests."
    fr "J’y arriverai un jour. C’est juste difficile de trouver des gens sympas qui partagent tes centres d’intérêt."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip4.rpy:44
translate french marip4_0b4501cf:

    # fr "Anyways. Let's talk about something else."
    fr "Bref. Parlons d’autre chose."

